d <PERSON> Ramos </PERSON> was apprehended after threatening the mayor and a pellet gun was confiscated. <PERSON> John </PERSON> <PERSON> Gentzler </PERSON>, <PERSON> Ramos </PERSON>' boss at <ORGANIZATION> York </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Snacks </ORGANIZATION>, said he worried about <PERSON> Ramos </PERSON>, but not that he might hurt someone. `` He tells me he had no friends,'' <PERSON> Gentzler </PERSON> said. `` I knew he needed some help, so I reached out to him as a father figure.'' <PERSON> Gentzler </PERSON> said <PERSON> Ramos </PERSON>, who worked the overnight shift, got along well with employees. He did have `` a little verbal battle with a few workers'' early Wednesday, but <PERSON> Gentzler </PERSON> said he did n't think it was anything to worry about.
